                     <interp inst="t18440408-1140-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing 2 pairs of stays, value 9<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18440408-name-682" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18440408-name-682" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18440408-name-682" type="surname" value="LONGLAND"></interp>
